{
  "stem": "11771.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they have new victims, and they start to get rid of us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we got our portion already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They tell us to rest ourselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the meanwhile, in the pause from us to the second group what's going to happen, they went to drink beer and to smoke cigars.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the window, the guy who came in with the new group, he start to, to scream and to curse. 'So much smoke here.' They used to smoke cigars.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he opens up the window to let the smoke out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he went back to, to the new group he brought in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't see how many he-- or how much he brought in, but they were standing outside in the second room.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When the rest undressed and they told us to dressed up, I didn't dressed up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When I found the seconds, the minutes while they were dressing and changing the guards-- they went out to drink beer in the second room-- and he opened up the window to, to get out the smoke-- and I take a jump through the window.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I don't know where I'm going to jump.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know the circumstances of the building.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I just remember I was about 10, 12 steps up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I fell down, and it was a soft [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] ground.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was like-- and it was also in, in, in September.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was after a rain.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, it was the ground-- this was a garden there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "After me, Teivele, Teivele Blacha jumped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he got to start yell and, and screaming.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He broke-- he broke a leg while he was jumping.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they wouldn't know another two minutes that we disappeared if he would be successful to jump like me.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
